name: New Star Rubber Works
overview: New Star Rubber Works is a sole proprietorship based business venture, which was incorporated in the year 2010 at Chennai, Tamil Nadu. We are one of the prominent manufacturers and suppliers of a wide range of Rubber Sheets, U Seals, Conveyor Belts, Spare Tyre Couplings, Chevron Packings and many more. We design and develop our entire product line as per the prescribed industrial guidelines. These products are the first choice of millions of clients based across the country for their unsurpassed quality standards and some dynamic features such as sturdy construction, dimensional accuracy, precise designs, smooth operations, optimum performance, long service life, anti-corrosive finish, high tensile strength and durability. Our clients can avail these products from us in both standardized as well as customized form as per their specific demands and requirements.
